caption.title: mAb Gn3 and Gn32 neutralize RVFV in two serum neutralization tests.
caption.p: Data are shown as percentage neutralization and a regression model is fitted using 4-Parameter Logistic. (A) SNT using RVFV- strain MP-12. (B) SNT using RVFV- strain 35/74 Experiments were performed in duplicate.
